18 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 20 O.S. 2021, Section 91.7, is
19 amended to read as follows:
20 Section 91.7. A. The Oklahoma Legislature finds that, due to
21 the complex nature of litigation involving highly technical
22 commercial issues, there is a need for a court in Oklahoma's most
23 populated counties with specific jurisdiction over actions involving
24 such commercial issues.
