17 Vacancy Appointments. The Committee shall be responsible for
18 providing the Governor with a list of five nominees for judicial
19 appointment to each business court. The Governor shall appoint one
20 of the five nominees to the business court to preside as the
21 business court judge. The Committee shall consist of ten (10)
22 members, to be appointed as follows:
23 1. Five members of the Senate to be appointed by the President
24 Pro Tempore of the Oklahoma State Senate. Four of the members shall
